					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I liked it. It was very engaging. I upvoted it. I especially liked the characterization of 3744. I could really sympathize with 3744. It flowed very well and made sense. Of course he limited his powers to DnD. It makes sense. It was a bit sad and also a bit amusing. Of course he got some &quot;murder-hobos&quot;. Ah, this SCP reminds me of some of the DnD stories I've read online in the best way. I like everything about this.</p> 
				 	]]>
