					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7415347#post-3963284</guid>
				<title>#Team Sugary Sweet</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7415347/scp-3744#post-3963284</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 09 Sep 2018 03:44:41 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>JanitorCakeworth</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3484414</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>A big, big thank you to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/keyii" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4420424&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536465180" alt="keyii" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4420424)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/keyii" >keyii</a></span> for co-authoring this with me, helping me with 3744's character and whatnot. Team Sugary Sweet for life! #diabetesisaseriousproblem</p> <p>So, I was really, really unhappy with the reception of the previous SCP-3744, and I wanted to make amends. I didn't feel like this SCP was worth your time. So hopefully I've fixed that right up.</p> <p>The following are a bunch of folks who gave crits to this SCP: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536465180" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=414239&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536465180" alt="Gabriel Jade" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=414239)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" >Gabriel Jade</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/eskobar" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1173523&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536465180" alt="Eskobar" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1173523)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/eskobar" >Eskobar</a></span> <span class=